properties.sfomuseum:description: Amenity kit produced by United Airlines with multiple parts:a. Half moon shape navy blue textured bag with top zipper, navy blue acetate lining.b. Pair of navy blue sleep socks with a navy blue paper band with small double “U” airline logo with “United Airlines” on center.c. Sealed small clear plastic package with small double “U” airline logo with “United Airlines” near top edge, white paper tissues. d. Navy blue sleep mask in a clear plastic sleeve, small navy blue paper tag with white double “U” airline logo on edge of sleep mask.e. Sealed in clear plastic bag, black plastic toothbrush.f. Black and white emory board. g. Dark gray paper packet with small white double “U” airline logo and “United Airlines” on center, containing a toothpick and floss. h. White plastic tube of Rembrandt whitening toothpaste.i. Small clear plastic bottle of Rembrandt mouth rinse.j. Pair of earplugs in white paper container, small navy blue double “U” and “United Airlines” on center.k. Small clear plastic bottle of Molton Brown body lotion.l. Small short plastic jar of Molton Brown lip balm.m. Razor request card.
